        "rich_text_jpVFdD": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Navratri is not just a festival, it is an ode and tribute to all the powerful women. </p><p>Navratri is about worshipping goddesses - Durga, Lakshmi, and Saraswati - all of them representing the different aspects of strength,  courage, prosperity, and knowledge or wisdom. It calls for a tradition of gifting women who uplift you - may it be your sister, mother, friend or wife. This tradition is symbolic of  the good luck and uplifting that these women bring to life.</p><p>Unbreakable, pure, and brilliantly radiant, diamond jewellery mirrors the divine strength and timeless worth of the goddess-like women around you. Diamond jewellery makes a bold and graceful statement, perfect for festive jewellery. Here are some Navratri jewellery gift ideas that reflect your gratitude and love towards these women.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
